title: Gorilla Accountant
description:
Gorilla Accountant, written by Caitlin Tegart & David C. White. Stone Cold Fox at Maude Night, UCBTNY, April 14, 2008.

Starring Scott Courlander, D'Arcy Erokan & Cody Melton. Directed by Dominic Dierkes.
